name: Tucano do bico de ouro
description: Legend has it in the Juréia-Itatins region on the south coast of São Paulo, Brazil, that a golden toucan appears every seven years making a flight from Morro do Pogoçá to the Juréia massif, returning seven years later, and so on. And that the person who has vision of the golden toucan will be a rich and happy man.<Crypto Legends | A Series by Renancio Monte | 2021>
